OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FStrawberry growers in West Sussex are
OL,7,Fthe first in the world to use a
OL,8,Fparticular kind of climate control to
OL,9,Fgrow summer berries in the winter.
OL,11,FThe UK is largely self-sufficient in
OL,12,Fstrawberries from May to October, but
OL,13,Fthis new LED technology means that
OL,14,Fstrawberries can now be grown all year
OL,15,Fround.
OL,17,FThe glasshouse in Colworth near
OL,18,FChichester is the size of 10 football
OL,19,Fpitches and big enough to harvest
OL,20,Fstrawberries to fill one and a half
OL,21,Fmillion punnets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
