OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FThe Summer Berry Company is harnessing
OL,7,Frobotics and green energy to extend
OL,8,Fthe curfew of one of our favourite
OL,9,Ffruits.
OL,11,FThe investment reduces the site's
OL,12,Freliance on fossil fuels, with the
OL,13,Fsystem using a mix of renewable heat
OL,14,Fand power, LED lighting and energy
OL,15,Fstorage to recreate spring conditions
OL,16,Findoors.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
