PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FBartosz Pinkosz, UK operations
OL,7,Fdirector at The Summer Berry Company,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Typically, the demand for
OL,9,Fwinter strawberries has been fulfilled
OL,10,Fby flying them in from countries like
OL,11,FEgypt and Jordan but we believe our
OL,12,Fnew technology provides a far superior-
OL,13,Ftasting fruit which is less energy
OL,14,Fintensive to grow at our farm in West
OL,15,FSussex."
OL,17,FThe project uses 2,600 LED lights to
OL,18,Fcreate artificial sunlight and heat
OL,19,Fthe greenhouse to around 20 degree
OL,20,FCelsius.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
