PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FAs a result, the industry is expecting
OL,7,Fto produce fruit over winter of higher
OL,8,Fquality than typical Egyptian or
OL,9,FSpanish imports while potentially
OL,10,Fcutting around 400 tonnes brought in
OL,11,Ffrom overseas.
OL,13,FThe year-round operation is also
OL,14,Fsupporting stable, local employment as
OL,15,Fthe Chichester glasshouse has provided
OL,16,Fcontinuous work as opposed to purely
OL,17,Fseasonal for around 20 harvest
OL,18,Fworkers, 15 husbandry workers, five
OL,19,Fworkers in the packhouse and one
OL,20,Fstudent, and an agronomy and
OL,21,Fmanagement team of about 10 people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
