PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FHelen Wilson, Corporate services
OL,7,Fdirector at The Summer Berry Company,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We pride ourselves on this all
OL,9,Fyear round supply so that people in
OL,10,Fthe supermarket can choose to have a
OL,11,Flocally grown British berry that they
OL,12,Fknow will taste just like it would do
OL,13,Fin the summer.
OL,15,F"And we're not just relying on imports
OL,16,Ffrom other countries that might not
OL,17,Fhave such high quality and certainly
OL,18,Fwon't have been picked either that day
OL,19,For maybe the day before."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
