PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772885578
OL,3,CNew technology in Sussex means
OL,4,Cstrawberries can be grown during winter
OL,6,FAmong the strawberry varieties grown
OL,7,Fin Chichester are: Malling Ace,
OL,8,FKarima, Favori, Florice, Limore One
OL,9,Fand Fandango ` the last of which was
OL,10,Frecently recognised as one of the
OL,11,Ftastiest strawberries in the world
OL,12,Fafter receiving the top three-star
OL,13,FSuperior Taste Award from an
OL,14,Finternational panel of chefs and
OL,15,Fsommeliers.
OL,17,FThe berries will be stocked in all
OL,18,Fmajor supermarkets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
